This directory contains a handful of autobuild.sh script illustrating
recipes for different build systems

 - autobuild-autoconf.sh - from the libvirt project. Illustrates autoconf
   autobuild, libtool in a big C program

 - autobuld-perl-makemaker.sh - from this project. Illustrates ExtUtils::MakeMaker
   in a Perl program

 - autobuild-python.sh - from python-virtinst. Illustrates distutils in a
   Python program

